{"tid":487793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老港商投資印尼疑遭無辜判囚17年屢求助港府中國不果","createTime":"2017-12-03T05:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T08:58:16.000Z","uid":30169,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"675a8a326e44795dec75c4bd82d4285b402a1a6b","tid":487793,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T05:59:41.000Z","msg":"老港商投資印尼疑遭無辜判囚17年　子稱印檢察人員曾促金錢「解決」　屢求助港府中國不果<br />\n<br />\n街工接獲一名在印尼投資採礦業的七旬香港商人求助，指他在2014年起無辜遭當地檢察院指涉嫌貪污和行賄，多次被問話並被視為疑犯，至去年底被拘留，更遭改控「給國家造成財政虧損」，於9月初被判囚17年。<br />\n<br />\n被囚的是72歲商人林仲山，其兩名兒子今日在街工梁耀忠陪同下開記者會，稱父親已在印尼投資30年，自父親去年12月被印尼當局拘留起，曾尋求香港入境處、中國駐印尼大使館及駐泗水領事館的協助，回港後又在特首梁振英開行政會議前向他遞信，但各方均無提供具體協助，事件不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n他們又指出，父親在當地有繳足相關稅款及費用並有文件證明，但印尼的法庭審訊其父親時，不接納證人及辯方的證供和證據，又透露父親被調查時收到多名自稱印尼檢察院人員的來電，暗示私下見面後指支付一定金錢「去解決件事」，令林仲山無罪釋放，但林仲山拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他們指父親相信「一帶一路」國策，雖受印尼當局的調查，但仍繼續在當地投資，並加強與中國企業合作，並就兩地投資會見中國官員</strong></span>。他們均批評港府近年推廣「一帶一路」的好處，但忽略好像林仲山事件般對港人的保障。<br />\n<br />\n林仲山兒子林子溢說，父親最近一次回港是2015年年初，他指曾勸當時不斷受查的父親不要再去印尼，但當時父親認為在印尼可獲公平審訊，但至今無再回港。<br />\n<br />\n協助林仲山及其家人的街工立法會議員梁耀忠批評，特區政府積極推動「一帶一路」，但並無在香港介紹沿線國家的法治及政府結構問題，中國及香港政府在事件中亦無在外交上協助，擔心港人投資者在未來有多大保障。他希望特區政府協助此案中的人士，並在「一帶一路」下保障港人的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n入境處回覆查詢時表示，自接獲當事人家屬求助後，一直與外交部駐港特派員公署及中國駐泗水總領事館緊密聯繫，入境處多次透過總領館反映當事人及家屬的訴求，並透過總領館要求印尼有關部門保障當事人的合法權益，包括於獄中獲得合理待遇及合適的治療等。總領館人員亦曾數次到法庭旁聽審訊，敦促當地有關部門公正處理案件。入境處稱與總領館一直有跟家人保持聯絡，並會繼續與他們、公署及總領館保持密切聯繫提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦回覆查詢時則表示，已收到相關求助個案，並已按既定機制交由入境處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00001/1480587438991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480587438991&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX22i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=297463d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480587438991&h=9e45b8e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00001/1480587438991</a>[/quote]"},{"pid":"01a450a438c66fc973abe4b4a34d116594c4fb5a","tid":487793,"uid":30169,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:02:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他們指父親相信「一帶一路」國策，雖受印尼當局的調查，但仍繼續在當地投資，並加強與中國企業合作，並就兩地投資會見中國官員。他們均批評港府近年推廣「一帶一路」的好處</span>"},{"pid":"4a170849ee072e8ae4c2a3d3d12df0703b91d947","tid":487793,"uid":3109,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:03:55.000Z","msg":"條路自己揀, _ _ _ _ _<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bead816bbabaa6a12b5d546a1fbd9073d661c4aa","tid":487793,"uid":31887,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:05:16.000Z","msg":"中國都信<br />\n不如搵老千幫你投資啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcc22f7c210cf10707023de96c514030197a543","tid":487793,"uid":35014,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:08:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cbf51b927155f9286e4af63fa67d6a97d958f2ef","tid":487793,"uid":35870,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有讀中國歷史都知，明清一路以黎嘅外交政策，都係唔會理身在外地嘅商人利益<br />\n<br />\n唔似得英國佬，英國商人係外地畀人恰，即刻send隊fleet去保護<br />\n<br />\nThis is China <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5afc68c649ad7532e8605609b239bd91b480f857","tid":487793,"uid":22858,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/30/081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F30%2F081643_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=3be43dfc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b0a6a78135041230464eec3af0e1db8610a46d8","tid":487793,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"犯我中華者，雖遠必誅！！<br />\n<br />\n中華人民共和国公民：當你在海外遭遇危險，不要放棄！請記住，在你身後，有一個強大的祖國！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c05b9f79495a3146dd57a48d8ab4863ba53cfee1","tid":487793,"uid":62599,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:15:27.000Z","msg":"吳京去救人未？"},{"pid":"186216b569c4d7e9b1faf9e6c6a4b672f0aa37ee","tid":487793,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:22:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n比啲時間啦，一帶一路岩岩出冇耐，<br />\n<br />\n過多3 5 年隨時奉你為上賓"},{"pid":"25b7f91496720232e94ba8940d66440996167144","tid":487793,"uid":6752,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:24:34.000Z","msg":"大聲叫反共即刻有洗頭艇接送"},{"pid":"710b6e982e9afbc6d89a633f0834699a14e3ae9f","tid":487793,"uid":79919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:27:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>條路自己揀, _ _ _ _ _<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6caa538f65096559514567826cbdc0425b6440d","tid":487793,"uid":108022,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:32:00.000Z","msg":"in 支那he trust<br />\n下聯：自己攞泥賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"595028ced300e3a54c833da133926470cfaf9e4a","tid":487793,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:36:31.000Z","msg":"抵撚死啦,咁撚柒蠢唔死都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86db505050de3041bad35d933019aaed43f52602","tid":487793,"uid":11148,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:37:33.000Z","msg":"當時父親認為在印尼可獲公平審訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6feacc40c5fcfc94e634dbc313b41760ed2bb4b3","tid":487793,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:38:12.000Z","msg":"明明用錢解決到都死攬住唔放 咁抵你坐啦"},{"pid":"c183a7b4df831f5f9db32b5f3713689ef970cdd9","tid":487793,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52cae87a3e296ada55b7b77f9a1a75db304a76c8","tid":487793,"uid":51932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:41:49.000Z","msg":"唔驚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70a8e7440c49c72f5b3c5d4cd4f874c41256fc9d","tid":487793,"uid":20241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當時父親認為在印尼可獲公平審訊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年紀大個腦壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbe77733122bdda692d575df4310ea9454fddcdf","tid":487793,"uid":10757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T06:55:51.000Z","msg":"但印尼的法庭審訊其父親時，不接納證人及辯方的證供和證據，又透露父親被調查時收到多名自稱印尼檢察院人員的來電，暗示私下見面後指支付一定金錢「去解決件事」，令林仲山無罪釋放，但林仲山拒絕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比錢搞得掂 點解仲要政府幫呢"},{"pid":"8bda6b29391d7d5bf35c35bc11fa7d6e59b24694","tid":487793,"uid":39846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:46:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但印尼的法庭審訊其父親時，不接納證人及辯方的證供和證據，又透露父親被調查時收到多名自稱印尼檢察院人員的來電，暗示私下見面後指支付一定金錢「去解決件事」，令林仲山無罪釋放，但林仲山拒絕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比錢搞得掂 點解仲要政府幫呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇權冇勢比左都未必有用。揾支共就仲仆街，政府中間嗰班，打個電話都可能要左你幾球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。"},{"pid":"e18420c2417e4fa32f444a86c1dbfcb81fbfafa6","tid":487793,"uid":58889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T07:48:56.000Z","msg":"一賄一賂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fde1ae42b158763c582137355f5c3c5cdc1dd4ac","tid":487793,"uid":12757,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老港商投資印尼疑遭無辜判囚17年　子稱印檢察人員曾促金錢「解決」　屢求助港府中國不果<br />\n<br />\n街工接獲一名在印尼投資採礦業的七旬香港商人求助，指他在2014年起無辜遭當地檢察院指涉嫌貪污和行賄，多次被問話並被視為疑犯，至去年底被拘留，更遭改控「給國家造成財政虧損」，於9月初被判囚17年。<br />\n<br />\n被囚的是72歲商人林仲山，其兩名兒子今日在街工梁耀忠陪同下開記者會，稱父親已在印尼投資30年，自父親去年12月被印尼當局拘留起，曾尋求香港入境處、中國駐印尼大使館及駐泗水領事館的協助，回港後又在特首梁振英開行政會議前向他遞信，但各方均無提供具體協助，事件不了了之。<br />\n<br />\n他們又指出，父親在當地有繳足相關稅款及費用並有文件證明，但印尼的法庭審訊其父親時，不接納證人及辯方的證供和證據，又透露父親被調查時收到多名自稱印尼檢察院人員的來電，暗示私下見面後指支付一定金錢「去解決件事」，令林仲山無罪釋放，但林仲山拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>他們指父親相信「一帶一路」國策，雖受印尼當局的調查，但仍繼續在當地投資，並加強與中國企業合作，並就兩地投資會見中國官員</strong></span>。他們均批評港府近年推廣「一帶一路」的好處，但忽略好像林仲山事件般對港人的保障。<br />\n<br />\n林仲山兒子林子溢說，父親最近一次回港是2015年年初，他指曾勸當時不斷受查的父親不要再去印尼，但當時父親認為在印尼可獲公平審訊，但至今無再回港。<br />\n<br />\n協助林仲山及其家人的街工立法會議員梁耀忠批評，特區政府積極推動「一帶一路」，但並無在香港介紹沿線國家的法治及政府結構問題，中國及香港政府在事件中亦無在外交上協助，擔心港人投資者在未來有多大保障。他希望特區政府協助此案中的人士，並在「一帶一路」下保障港人的人身安全。<br />\n<br />\n入境處回覆查詢時表示，自接獲當事人家屬求助後，一直與外交部駐港特派員公署及中國駐泗水總領事館緊密聯繫，入境處多次透過總領館反映當事人及家屬的訴求，並透過總領館要求印尼有關部門保障當事人的合法權益，包括於獄中獲得合理待遇及合適的治療等。總領館人員亦曾數次到法庭旁聽審訊，敦促當地有關部門公正處理案件。入境處稱與總領館一直有跟家人保持聯絡，並會繼續與他們、公署及總領館保持密切聯繫提供協助。<br />\n<br />\n特首辦回覆查詢時則表示，已收到相關求助個案，並已按既定機制交由入境處跟進。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00001/1480587438991\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480587438991&d=7yrBVEiWxAMk2TXQ7%2BGX22i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=297463d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20161201%2Fs00001%2F1480587438991&h=9e45b8e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20161201/s00001/1480587438991</a></blockquote>[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n收皮啦梁耀忠   咁撚怕事學咩撚野幫人出頭 仲學人做立法會議員  <br />\n就係呢條垃圾助長建制派"},{"pid":"78aca096d1cf006431816b1b05a2e25150be6ea7","tid":487793,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但印尼的法庭審訊其父親時，不接納證人及辯方的證供和證據，又透露父親被調查時收到多名自稱印尼檢察院人員的來電，暗示私下見面後指支付一定金錢「去解決件事」，令林仲山無罪釋放，但林仲山拒絕。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比錢搞得掂 點解仲要政府幫呢</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n冇權冇勢比左都未必有用。揾支共就仲仆街，政府中間嗰班，打個電話都可能要左你幾球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就抵佢喇 以前英國政府都可能9up下...依家... d阿伯都唔撚化"},{"pid":"a921610387c78cdb9ee112ea7927ae3035abca91","tid":487793,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T08:35:43.000Z","msg":"我自己推測佢係想支共出頭幫佢傾話俾左一定放人<br />\n一陣俾左滅埋你口仲衰<br />\n點知無人濕佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}